/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChing ho ball"},{"pid":"352f4b278f50f3870bf4a819a6607233d0f40a52","tid":512641,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T18:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/024010_ee356e00f33fe93d69e2d05aa801a733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F024010_ee356e00f33fe93d69e2d05aa801a733.jpg&h=a361763d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我都係<br />\n早半個月篤拇指<br />\n果星期係三份一隻手掌有瘀血<br />\n捽散左以為無事<br />\n但拇指連掌果節關節仍腫起<br />\n用力會痛<br />\n拉到某啲位會痛<br />\n準備聽日睇跌打"},{"pid":"4bc5d6c67096054dee74ff1d8725479f5a6cd429","tid":512641,"uid":108562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣 又係篤完又篤 冇去睇鐵打 最後屈唔到先去睇 佢話篤完之後啲骨彎左跟住唔理佢啲搞到啲骨生硬番 隻手指伸唔番直 要做手術先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a8c2467400960b87c028f19c346e9c407c64aa","tid":512641,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T19:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同你一樣 又係篤完又篤 冇去睇鐵打 最後屈唔到先去睇 佢話篤完之後啲骨彎左跟住唔理佢啲搞到啲骨生硬番 隻手指伸唔番直 要做手術先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adbac649ed7e294cc450d48fba46011d06d8e68","tid":512641,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T19:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/lbra3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2Flbra3.jpg&h=63958870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無名指仲粗過中指<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>當初又唔即刻睇，傻下傻下<br />\n<br />\n呢啲要幾年先會消<br />\n<br />\n你去邊度睇都無乜用<br />\n<br />\n有錢就去睇下跌打啦</blockquote><br />\n平時篤開 無諗過會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ebffef26285e3e3a35f9b9fa