citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦，以後仲有9隻可以用"},{"pid":"d8d95ce8c4c9b78995a49c681774b0be8cebe1ea","tid":512641,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>切得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n組織壞死<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/112234_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F112234_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=641ec926&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213e04d0c01a9f4ff33c7c7e4a43091b9e4eeb1a","tid":512641,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"總之就去睇下醫生先，你信跌打或西醫都無所謂，總之問下專業意見先<br />\n<br />\n輕則只是關節與關節之間傷左軟組織<br />\n但呢個係好難好返<br />\n<br />\n我相信你現在揸拳頭都有困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c967b9f21c60c453a40f88db02f8f1d0e5f6be","tid":512641,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"用藥酒摔下佢就得啦"},{"pid":"1d0eec26e4788f7500f3892912f0f6e07f34c665","tid":512641,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:58:48.000Z","msg":"1.你隻手指腫左超過2個禮拜都唔知有問題<br />\n2.竟然腫左2個月先覺得有問題<br />\n3.覺得有問題竟然唔係睇醫生, 而係上連登開post問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都唔知點話你好。。"},{"pid":"f9e1aae61a48f81f61ea5806337bc4dd20c7632e","tid":512641,"uid":38725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"祝福樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e24843be9514110db4f8bcc71dcb564eac0931","tid":512641,"uid":107611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"千其唔好睇醫生!<br />\n去埋u汪 香討 高登問埋先!"},{"pid":"39983affd9dbd0b70bf726c7a2ff92f7c2dc8708","tid":512641,"uid":91833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係唔信中醫跌打咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做乜又選擇性失明"},{"pid":"e51487a56e8603b4aaa1ae0a1dfe6f34ca79dce4","tid":512641,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"等多一年就會好返"},{"pid":"b7880b71dea2bb23e71bea38b68c07e4bf07aab0","tid":512641,"uid":56717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"認真，伸唔直屈唔埋，有時係太腫阻住，但係咁耐都未好，似入面韌帶斷/裂左多d，早少少去睇我諗醫生/Physio 會比個類似夾ge 物體你夾住手指，等佢入面生番埋。不過過左咁耐唔知仲有冇用，話唔定已經生埋左/生到亂左。<br />\n<br />\n之旦係你又未消到腫，你都係快手去睇physio/醫生啦<br />\n<br />\n利申: 試過"},{"pid":"964abc1fa1d4885409a80e8bc582d4140e9d86ea","tid":512641,"uid":56717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7880b71dea2bb23e71bea38b68c07e4bf07aab0","tid":512641,"uid":56717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"認真，伸唔直屈唔埋，有時係太腫阻住，但係咁耐都未好，似入面韌帶斷/裂左多d，早少少去睇我諗醫生/Physio 會比個類似夾ge 物體你夾住手指，等佢入面生番埋。不過過左咁耐唔知仲有冇用，話唔定已經生埋左/生到亂左。<br />\n<br />\n之旦係你又未消到腫，你都係快手去睇physio/醫生啦<br />\n<br />\n利申: 試過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"補充，唔知你邊個位傷啦，你可以試下用另一隻手，比少少力壓住受傷手指，同時受傷手指又試下出力反抗，如果有力但唔係太大力，咁有機會只係裂左，但如果完全無力反抗就真係斷曬。1999 希望你明我講咩"},{"pid":"27078773be209ba6e5cfbf028ccdc44a4d119504","tid":512641,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"唔該哂bro<br />\n九龍區 邊間睇得過？"},{"pid":"da910050d66c54fa4bd6494fb43d820b20f0f0b7","tid":512641,"uid":16710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"我都係2個月前篤到中指無名指，又係依節腫但無你咁勁，我睇左一次跌打，之後睇西醫做物理治療，消左啲腫不過屈埋有拉痛感，照過x光骨無事，應該係軟組織同韌帶發炎，你要去睇下醫生先睇下d骨有無移位，同埋用運動膠布包住果個關節位唔好專登去屈佢拉佢，等佢慢慢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}